node.text: Feelin good after lasts race p7 finish!! Back to @darlingtonraceway here we go👊 @ford @monsterenergy

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hailie Deegan on August 26, 2021 tagging @rambodeegan. May be an image of 1 person and animal.

node.text: #HappyNationalDogDay to my high maintenance epileptic lil tyrant ❤️ Never thought I could love a dog so much till I got him. He has put me through hell in back from scaring me with seizures to literally 💩 on me but I love him so much so I’ll take it😂. @rambodeegan

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hailie Deegan on August 23, 2021 tagging @engineice. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Only the best when it comes to my vehicles 🙌 @engineice

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hailie Deegan on August 21, 2021 tagging @fordperformance. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: @ford if you ever feel the need to get rid of any of these cars make sure I’m at the top of that list 😂 #woodwarddreamcruise

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hailie Deegan in World Wide Technology Raceway with @monsterenergy, @fordperformance, @simpsonraceproducts, @engineice, and @wastequip.llc. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Man what a night! So beyond happy we were able to put a good run together finishing p7. Going into this race I made some new goals for myself and one of those was to get as many top 10s to finish out this season as I can. This is just the beginning 🙌 @ford @monsterenergy
